The,Free,Currency,Converter,API,allows,users,to,convert,from,one,currency,to,another,Currency,values,are,updated,every,minutes,and,queries,accept,a,maximum,of,conversion,parameters,If,users,need,more,frequent,value,updates,or,additional,conversion,parameters,they,can,contact,the,API,provider,for,more,information,Developers,are,free,to,use,the,Free,Currency,Converter,for,either,personal,or,commercial,applications,No,warranty,is,provided